	<a name="post145060"></a>
	
	<font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" ><b>Riverdane</b></font><br>
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" >Forum Wizard</font><br>
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" ></font><br>
	<p>
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" >Server: Vazaelle<br>
	Guild: <br>
	<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=&resize=true" target=_blank>Magelo Profile</a><br>
	</font></td>
	
	<td bgcolor="#F1F1F1" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" > <b></b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >Darkness.<br />
<br />
Then....blue light.....blinding, electric blue, shining like a blue sun, so bright Camille has to raise her hand to her eyes.<br />
<br />
Slowly the light dims, shrinks...takes form...a gem, a blue gemstone, the size of her fist, beautifully cut, laying on a pillow of black velvet. She reaches out, picking the gem up from its bed.<br />
<br />
Something is moving in the gem.<br />
<br />
A dark spot inside the gem, moving. Intrigued, she brings the gem close to her face, peering inside to see what it is, uneasiness not quelling the curiosity that has risen in her.<br />
<br />
Suddenly, with a small thump, a figure inside the gem slams up against the edge, face and fists pressed up darkly against the crystal walls. Riverdane, tiny, but recognizable, banging again and again on the walls of the gem, eyes wild and staring right through her.<br />
<br />
"VEN...!" he begins to scream, and is drowned out, as Camille, horrified, joins with him, and the sound of her shrieks the only thing left that she hears.</font></p>
	
