<table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td width="10"><img width="10" height="1" src="images/space.gif" alt=""></td><td width="100%"><!-- spacer -->

<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#555576"  width="100%" align="center"><tr><td>
<table cellpadding="4" cellspacing="1" border="0"  width="100%">
<tr>
	<td bgcolor="#DFDFDF" width="175" valign="top" nowrap>
	<a name="post147709"></a>
	
	<font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" ><b>Riverdane</b></font><br>
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" >Forum Wizard</font><br>
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" ></font><br>
	<p>
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" >Server: Vazaelle<br>
	Guild: <br>
	<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=&resize=true" target=_blank>Magelo Profile</a><br>
	</font></td>
	
	<td bgcolor="#DFDFDF" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" > <b></b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >"Where do I begin?" Vven asked, "Greig, damned, I didn't think I would be asked about him ever. Who's been talking to you about him, and why? Vindayyan? Dooma? Moelle? We had made a pact not to talk about it to anyone, but who can trust dark elves?" He laughed ironically. <br />
<br />
"None of them." Camille said, "It was Terris."<br />
<br />
"Terris?" Vven laughed, then stopped abruptly, searching Camille's face for a lie. Camille just nodded slowly. "That bitch. She DID pick my head, then. I knew it."<br />
<br />
Vven whistled sharply towards the bar. Within seconds an ire ghast bearing a tray of six mugs of ale appeared at the table and set them before the party. Rocsalt and Verdad took their mugs up, while Camille, Grelin and Talvarien let theirs sit. Vven took his mug and drained in down in one long quaff.<br />
<br />
"Ok, let's see." Vven began, staring at the empty mug. "It was a while ago, a year? Year and a half maybe before the whole End Game thing. I was on a double date with my pal Vindayyan, this dark elf shadowknight I was was guilded with at the time. Sort of like River but blue and bloodthirsty. I was dating Dooma, this inky cleric, and Vinny was with this teir'dal wizard chick, Moelle. Both of us thought we were getting laid for sure that night, until the girls show up, and Dooma introduces her idiot cousin Randolf, a....hells, I forget his class. Probably didn't have a class, too damned stupid to learn one. The kid was sort of gangly and awkward for a dark elf, and...slow, I guess is the word. Freakin' moron, would laugh like an idiot, even if no one was saying anything. Me and Vinny exchange looks cause with Happy the Classless Dope with us, getting these chicks out of their gear and into the shadows was going to be more difficult than banking in Felwithe. But, we go out anyway, Vinny having brought two jugs of Black Poison, and the five of us head to the moon to see what trouble we can get into.<br />
<br />
Moe ports us into Dawnshroud Peaks cause she 'loves the wolves'. So we spend some time killing wolves, getting a little wasted on the Black, setting the wolves on fire and watching them run off howling, when this raid ports in. They're wearing a mix of armor, none of them looking like they could take on Crushbone with the way they're milling about and ignoring orders the leader is desperately calling out. We all are hiding, old dark elf trick, and none of them see us.<br />
<br />
'Pickup raid, looks like.' Vinny whispers to me, and I nod, smelling disaster. And then Vinny starts smiling all nasty like, and I'm smiling, and mouth 'Pickup raid' to the girls and now they're smiling, and Randolf, he's smiling cause he's an idiot, and then he starts with that stupid laugh of his, and Vinny kicks him till he shuts up.<br />
<br />
So, this raid finally gets its crap together, and we, too drunk to think twice about this, sorta mix ourselves in in the back. They don't even notice. And they start marching along a hillside, and end up in front of this old castle.<br />
<br />
In we go with the raid, and they are a freakin' mess. They have like three pullers and two tanks and the tanks are trying to plow by just marching ahead but the pullers are getting angry they aren't allowed to pull so they start pulling anyway, and pretty soon we're fighting mobs that we're walking into and mobs that are being added by the pullers and it's like a joke. At this point, just to keep US alive I'm mezzing like nuts, and Dooma is healing Vinny cause he's getting his hands in it, and Moe thank Inny ISN'T using areas for once. But it's pretty bad, and I'm pretty drunk. I don't know to this day how I was even able to cast, I was so gone from the booze. I was literally hallucinating. I'm looking at one of the tanks at one point and suddenly he looks like this minotaur, so I poke Vinny and point, and Vinny sticks him with the sword and he dies and then he looks like the tank again. Ooops, ah well. Black Poison is some strong crap, let me tell you.<br />
<br />
We stopped doing anything at that point, after we killed one of the raid, and just hung out in the back, watching. This raid would have wiped for sure if not for the size of it. And deeper and deeper into this place we go.<br />
<br />
Then we get to this one place where like four halls are intersecting and the raid is jamming in and I'm thinking, aggro city, they are gunna pull everything within 100 feet. So I grab the girls' wrists and pull them after me and Vinny into this one room we just cleared and wait. And Dooma's like 'Where's Randolf?' and Vinny sighes and rolls his eyes, while she goes off to find her cousin. After a moment she comes back with Idiot Boy, who's giggling and Vinny has to backhand him to shut him up, before the raid heard we were in the backroom and wondered why we weren't with the rest of them. So I pass around the bottle and we juice up, and wait. And sure enough after a few moments, we hear them start fighting and yelling add, add, add. I guess they lost their other chanter earlier or he gated or something, cause they keep yelling add add add and I just keep on drinking while they start screaming and this goes on for a while and then finally stops. <br />
<br />
After all the noise finished I invis up and check out the room. Everybody's dead, the mobs, the raid, everybody. There's more blood than when Vinny tried to pierce his ear with a dagger when we were kids. So I call in the rest of them to see, and Dooma goes 'Rezz them?' and I go 'Nah' and Vinny suggests, 'Loot the mobs?' and I go 'Yeah!'. So we start rummaging through the dead, but they don't have nothing, cept this one, has this key. And go figure, the room has a locked door. So I'm looking at Vinny going "Key?' and Vinny's wasted enough to say 'Sure.' so we put the key in the door and click we're in.<br />
<br />
Nothing in the room cept this big glowing gem, the size of man. And Randolf that idiot goes 'Oooh, sparkly!' and touches it, and POOF he disappears. Dooma starts cursing and saying we gotta go get him, so we all against our better judgement touch the gem and POOF we go too, into this room where Randolf is running around like the dope he is with three mobs on him. Now, we have a chanter, a tank, a cleric, a wiz and a moron, and it's only three mobs, so mezz mezz chop chop boom we kill them. Then Vinny kicks Randolf and Dooma kicks Randolf and we look around and see there's only one way out, through this door at the other room and up these steps. I'm thinking, let's just have Moe port us the hells out of here, but Vinny wants to look up the steps, so up we go."<br />
<br />
Vven stopped speaking for a moment, lost in thought. Then he pointed to Camille's untouched mug.<br />
<br />
"You going to drink that?" he asked. Camille shook her head.<br />
<br />
"Don't mind me." Vven said, picking it up and draining it. Then putting the empty mug down on the table, he continued.</font></p>
	
	<p></p>
	<p></p>
